      "reason" : "BIGGEST_MUSIC_LISTENING_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let indie pop pour from breakfast to brunch",
      "description" : "Your morning opened with a double shot of “Smooth Operator” before indie pop took over—again&again, TV Girl, and Djo weaving through a steady stream of “Big sip it or drip it.” By afternoon, you kept the tempo up with Good Kid and Surf Curse. 129 minutes, 45 tracks, 33 artists—your biggest music day, a seamless indie run.",
