      "title" : "The day you turned your queue into Soldier Field",
      "description" : "From midday through late evening, you dove deep into the world of the Chicago Bears, following every twist from a game-winning field goal to the hiring of Ben Johnson. Three episodes, one podcast, and not a single song in sight—just 165 minutes of Bears talk, your biggest podcast day of the year by far.",
